en_132203_0	Former president Mahinda Rajapaksa said he and some others will be taken to courts for taking part at the May Day rally organized by the Joint Opposition.
en_132203_1	He made this statement whilst addressing the gathering at the Lalith Athulathmudali grounds in Kirulapone yesterday.
en_132203_2	Forty Parliamentarians including Dalus Alahapperuma, Mahinda Yap Abewardena, Mahindananda Aluthgamage, Bandula Gunawardena and Pavithra Wanniarachchi participated at the rally.
en_132203_3	Politicos representing other parties were also seen at the event.
